    {
      "block_id": "doxlgiNsxk4kXlCrLq6mLMfhuH9",
      "block_type": 2,
      "block_type_name": "text",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "大家说小龙虾\"有灵魂\"，这个概念听起来很玄。",
          "style": {
            "bold": false,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "block_id": "doxlgMryDrmbBO1jgBZ7Hksxg4c",
      "block_type": 2,
      "block_type_name": "text",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "但实际上，所谓灵魂，就是把系统提示词里那一块，关于\"agent 是谁、行为风格是什么\"的内容，单独抽出来，存成一个 soul.md 文件。",
          "style": {
            "bold": false,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "block_id": "doxlgsHjn28wPLgen6E6MbWWsah",
      "block_type": 2,
      "block_type_name": "text",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "和 skill 的逻辑一模一样。以前每次要手动粘贴一大段 prompt 告诉 AI 怎么干事，现在把它固定成 .md 文件，agent 启动时自动读取。",
          "style": {
            "bold": false,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "Soul 就是这个思路用在人格设定上的版本。",
          "style": {
            "bold": true,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "block_id": "doxlgk0K1yh9t67J4WWh97wnyxc",
      "block_type": 2,
      "block_type_name": "text",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "所以你可以在社区里分享你的 soul.md，别人下载下来，agent 就有了你调好的风格。\"传播灵魂\"说的就是这件事。",
          "style": {
            "bold": false,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        }
      ]
    },
