        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "直播开始前，仓库只有中文版本的文件夹。20多分钟后，刷新页面，英语和日语两个版本的文件夹已经静静地出现在那里。",
          "style": {
            "bold": false,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "block_id": "doxlgWF6P0bKisTuVIGNZZEyDJe",
      "block_type": 2,
      "block_type_name": "text",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "\"我都没注意，它在后台自己干完了，直接提交了。\"",
          "style": {
            "bold": false,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "block_id": "doxlgI2Orb03ymkMgdbZ99xfhIe",
      "block_type": 2,
      "block_type_name": "text",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "WaytoAGI 社区在日本、新加坡都有很多朋友。小龙虾顺手把多语言版本搞定这件事，是本地部署最直观的价值体现。",
          "style": {
            "bold": false,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "block_id": "doxlgSlGOoOOXQi8zKfBqAUz6Ug",
      "block_type": 2,
      "block_type_name": "text",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "一周5000个 commit",
          "style": {
            "background_color": 15,
            "bold": true,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "text_color": 6,
            "underline": false
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "block_id": "doxlgTM0h1MWKyLr5NGpLDxiZOh",
      "block_type": 2,
      "block_type_name": "text",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "来新璐拉了 OpenClaw 的最新代码，",
          "style": {
            "bold": false,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "跟一周前对比，多了将近5000个 commit。",
          "style": {
            "bold": true,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "block_id": "doxlgyDefFaxjStke5kUGhjEGuo",
      "block_type": 2,
      "block_type_name": "text",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "换算一下：一家公司的工程师，平均每天提交十几到二十个 commit，连续干一年，才能积累5000个，而这个项目一周就到了。",
          "style": {
            "bold": false,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "block_id": "doxlghZrIvVeduqrRF7bg1BhzRd",
      "block_type": 2,
      "block_type_name": "text",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "\"这个项目99%是非人类在更新。\"",
          "style": {
            "bold": false,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "block_id": "doxlg3pHEMTmXe6RRzbDyszdaYf",
      "block_type": 2,
      "block_type_name": "text",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "项目作者 Kidd 肯定 review 不过来，大概率是让 agent 简单看一眼就 merge 了。这也解释了为什么最近不少用户遇到莫名其妙的 bug，过一两周更新一次通常就好了。",
          "style": {
            "bold": false,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "block_id": "doxlgPuPfjWUnwc5yc58h4kvFhg",
      "block_type": 2,
      "block_type_name": "text",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "用小龙虾打 FaceTime 连线网友",
          "style": {
            "background_color": 15,
            "bold": true,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "text_color": 6,
            "underline": false
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "block_id": "doxlg2cAjyOu6v3pqnsjATbJIoP",
      "block_type": 2,
      "block_type_name": "text",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "这是当晚最有节目效果的环节。",
          "style": {
            "bold": false,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "block_id": "doxlgOw5B03Hs4eNqlz0Z59l0af",
      "block_type": 2,
      "block_type_name": "text",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "来新璐想测试小龙虾能不能控制电脑打电话。他让 agent 给一位直播间网友打 FaceTime，发了一条消息，然后看着屏幕，FaceTime 应用窗口弹出来了，自动填入了对方号码，电话真的拨出去了！",
          "style": {
            "bold": false,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "block_id": "doxlg0Wmmf6CzdQfPB9rxVlerQc",
      "block_type": 2,
      "block_type_name": "text",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "网友陆萌接通后，被拉进直播做了一次即兴连线，当场向大家拜了个开春，AJ 说下次可以用这种方式连线了。",
          "style": {
            "bold": false,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "block_id": "doxlgf7uXEB823XFrXIyqYyfr7d",
      "block_type": 2,
      "block_type_name": "text",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "来新璐自己也没想到真的能成。",
          "style": {
            "bold": false,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "打电话这件事，agent 是靠 FaceTime 的命令行参数直接操作的，驱动它的是智谱的 GLM 模型，没有配置任何浏览器 MCP。",
          "style": {
            "bold": true,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "block_id": "doxlgksrZ89zduzLZVp7hCHOlEu",
      "block_type": 5,
      "block_type_name": "heading3",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "4. 几个值得记住的判断",
          "style": {
            "bold": false,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "block_id": "doxlgojtCFLghOaTXP9XEcmBR5b",
      "block_type": 2,
      "block_type_name": "text",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "本地部署 vs. 云端部署，差距很大。",
          "style": {
            "background_color": 15,
            "bold": true,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "text_color": 6,
            "underline": false
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "block_id": "doxlguE4PHDrOjGoHusvjzLUiRy",
      "block_type": 2,
      "block_type_name": "text",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "来新璐两周前在云服务器上部署过一版小龙虾，用了一段时间后放弃了。",
          "style": {
            "bold": false,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "block_id": "doxlgR6D6rl4Y8iOtKmWHzKiADg",
      "block_type": 2,
      "block_type_name": "text",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "把它部署在云服务器上，和用 Manus 基本没有区别。上面没有你的本地数据，没有你的文件，能干的事非常有限。",
          "style": {
            "bold": false,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "block_id": "doxlgfoaKsc6lKXv2lRL2IKEolf",
      "block_type": 2,
      "block_type_name": "text",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "部署在本地电脑上就是另一回事了。",
          "style": {
            "bold": false,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "block_id": "doxlgOrDr9hbOBZ7rJ7gaUHGMbh",
      "block_type": 2,
      "block_type_name": "text",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "它可以读你桌面上的所有文件，帮你清理磁盘、调整电池策略、找某个文件发给你，这些是云端做不到的。",
          "style": {
            "bold": false,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "block_id": "doxlg8JAxpBjkppCKonap1XmpRd",
      "block_type": 2,
      "block_type_name": "text",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "当然，权限越大，风险越大。",
          "style": {
            "bold": true,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "block_id": "doxlgbHsWjNJrF9pxRjDjlk5oOV",
      "block_type": 2,
      "block_type_name": "text",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "有次让 agent \"继续干你所有能干的事\"，结果它在清理磁盘的时候，差点把给甲方客户用的数据资料也删了。",
          "style": {
            "bold": false,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "block_id": "doxlgJ10PZ3wPYz0V4aPNB8Vqxb",
      "block_type": 2,
      "block_type_name": "text",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "\"你安全做得越好，小龙虾能干的事就越少；你安全做得越松，你不知道模型会不会干点意外的事情。\"",
          "style": {
            "bold": false,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "block_id": "doxlgd1RfBXlczkS6SG85sGWtLh",
      "block_type": 2,
      "block_type_name": "text",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "关于用哪个模型跑龙虾。",
          "style": {
            "background_color": 15,
            "bold": true,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "text_color": 6,
            "underline": false
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "block_id": "doxlgsgcsulTrEdSn1NwDlpNU9g",
      "block_type": 2,
      "block_type_name": "text",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "来新璐的建议是尽量用 Claude，驱动 agent 做复杂任务，模型能力的差距非常明显。",
          "style": {
            "bold": false,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "block_id": "doxlgi5Lzjm4Jix1P8wpLlrO9xc",
      "block_type": 2,
      "block_type_name": "text",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "国产模型也能跑，但他用某国产模型清理磁盘，agent 明明记录了每项清理了多少空间，最后汇报可用空间时却算错了，从原来的25G越算越小，变成了21G。",
          "style": {
            "bold": false,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "block_id": "doxlgabqJXMpR6Ali41LIFXy3Pf",
      "block_type": 2,
      "block_type_name": "text",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "不过如果只是用来跑通流程、熟悉机制，国产模型的 coding plan 是够用的。",
          "style": {
            "bold": false,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "block_id": "doxlgyxRkhKUIsQeTzP2maYdw2c",
      "block_type": 2,
      "block_type_name": "text",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "而且现在很多人都有 Claude Cod的订阅，可以把 agent core 那部分替换成 Claude Code CLI，复用订阅而不走 API 付费，成本更低。",
          "style": {
            "bold": false,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "block_id": "doxlg8kYraSukqos8JNjYoy2hve",
      "block_type": 2,
      "block_type_name": "text",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "看完这场，你会发现小龙虾没有那么神秘，但也不是说随便让它干就能干好。",
          "style": {
            "bold": false,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "block_id": "doxlgLgWHAV5UGr6MIChv2D8L5d",
      "block_type": 2,
      "block_type_name": "text",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "它的能力边界，",
          "style": {
            "bold": false,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "和你给它配了什么工具、用什么模型、部署在哪里，关系都很大。",
          "style": {
            "bold": true,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "block_id": "doxlgSI4t4LrOMlEoPJtiTA7eTe",
      "block_type": 2,
      "block_type_name": "text",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "现在最合适的姿势，可能就是先把它部署在自己的电脑上，把它当一个随时在后台帮你盯着事情、没事给自己找事干的搭档用起来，然后慢慢往上加扩展。",
          "style": {
            "bold": false,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}